 "end_time": 148.38,\n    "text": "它可以分成國家頂級運名和通用的頂級運名"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 148.38,\n    "end_time": 150.74,\n    "text": "那國家的上面就比較好記憶"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 150.74,\n    "end_time": 153.74,\n    "text": "你想中國它的一個英文是不是China"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 153.74,\n    "end_time": 156.44,\n    "text": "所以說寫就說寫成了CN"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 156.44,\n    "end_time": 159.18,\n    "text": "這個就是中國它的一個國家頂級運名"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 159.18,\n    "end_time": 161.0,\n    "text": "那美國呢是US"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 161.0,\n    "end_time": 163.2,\n    "text": "英國呢是UK"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 163.2,\n    "end_time": 167.28,\n    "text": "那在這三個裡面我們比較常見的初題方式"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 167.28,\n    "end_time": 168.64,\n    "text": "大陸數是考CN"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 168.64,\n    "end_time": 171.96,\n    "text": "你知道CN還代表的是中國就可以了"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 171.96,\n    "end_time": 174.72,\n    "text": "然後從用頂級運名是有四個"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 174.72,\n    "end_time": 177.92,\n    "text": "在這四個裡面比較常考的是前三個"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 177.92,\n    "end_time": 179.7,\n    "text": "那第一個這個COM"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 179.7,\n    "end_time": 181.8,\n    "text": "它就是公司企業"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 181.8,\n    "end_time": 184.76,\n    "text": "那這個EDU代表的就是交易機構"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 184.76,\n    "end_time": 186.5,\n    "text": "因為它是這個Ibuction"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 186.5,\n    "end_time": 188.44,\n    "text": "這個教育它的一個縮寫嘛"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 188.44,\n    "end_time": 191.16,\n    "text": "所以EDU代表的就是交易機構"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 191.16,\n    "end_time": 194.22,\n    "text": "那Gov代表的就是政府部門"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 194.22,\n    "end_time": 196.7,\n    "text": "同樣的也是這個英文Gavement"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 196.7,\n    "end_time": 198.56,\n    "text": "它的一個縮寫"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 199.28,\n    "end_time": 202.46,\n    "text": "所以這三個是要求大家一定要記住的"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 202.46,