ime": 802.92,\n    "knowledge_point": "应用层协议总结表",\n    "description": "总结常见应用层协议所使用的传输层协议（TCP/UDP）及对应端口号，强调该表格的重要性，作为解题的关键依据。"\n  },\n  {\n    "start_time": 803.84,\n    "end_time": 850.6,\n    "knowledge_point": "课程总结与练习题预告",\n    "description": "总结本节课内容，布置课后练习题，并预告下一节课程，鼓励学生复习巩固。"\n  }\n]'}], 'reasoning_content': '', 'role': 'assistant'}, 'finish_reason': 'stop'}]}, 'usage': {'total_tokens': 16670, 'input_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 15699}, 'output_tokens': 971, 'input_tokens': 15699, 'output_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 971}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'request_id': '90d75e3a-0649-41a2-9ae0-46f30cb3a9eb'}
