84,\n    "end_time": 850.6,\n    "knowledge_point": "课程总结与练习题预告",\n    "description": "总结本节课内容，布置课后练习题，并预告下一节课程，结束本节教学。"\n  }\n]'}], 'reasoning_content': '', 'role': 'assistant'}, 'finish_reason': 'stop'}]}, 'usage': {'total_tokens': 16593, 'input_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 15699}, 'output_tokens': 894, 'input_tokens': 15699, 'output_tokens_details': {'text_tokens': 894}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'request_id': 'd9fb3bd6-c689-4394-bd50-5ffbd8688885'}
